Package: HaploImputeR
Type: Package
Title: Haplotype Imputation and Generation Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("YUQI CHEN & YUNGANG", "HE", email = "625108562@qq.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Tools for haplotype imputation and generation using
    Lasso regression and probabilistic methods. This package provides
    functions to generate synthetic haplotypes based on reference
    population data while preserving allele frequency constraints.
    Includes support for dynamic window sizes based on LD structure,
    parallel processing for large datasets, and reproducible results
    through random seed control.
